## 📋 REMAINING FILES (9 files)

All remaining files follow the **exact same patterns** demonstrated in completed mockups.

### Operator Lead (3 more files)
**File:** `OperatorLead/press-analytics.html`
- **Purpose:** Press utilization analytics
- **Charts:**
  - Pie chart: Uptime vs Downtime per press
  - Bar chart: Jobs completed per press
  - Stacked bar chart: Downtime reasons
  - Line chart: Average cycle time trends
- **Pattern:** Same as MaterialHandlerLead/analytics.html
- **Mock Data:** Use `MockData.analytics.pressPerformance`

**File:** `OperatorLead/operator-management.html`
- **Purpose:** Operator roster and assignments
- **Components:**
  - Table: Operator name, assigned press, clock-in status, shift, actions
  - Status cards: Operators on floor, on break, total
  - Reassignment panel (similar to team-management.html)
- **Pattern:** Clone MaterialHandlerLead/team-management.html structure
- **Mock Data:** Use `MockData.pressOperators`

**File:** `OperatorLead/trends.html`
- **Purpose:** Historical performance trends
- **Charts:**
  - Line chart: Daily task volume (last 30 days)
  - Line chart: Average wait times over time
  - Bar chart: Monthly comparison (current vs previous)
  - Area chart: Operator productivity trends
- **Pattern:** Multiple line/area charts in 2x2 grid
- **Mock Data:** Generate time-series in JavaScript

### Plant Manager (5 files)
**File:** `PlantManager/dashboard.html`
- **Purpose:** Unified executive dashboard
- **Layout:**
  - Top: 6 KPI cards (MH tasks, Press tasks, Total operators, Total handlers, Avg efficiency, Critical items)
  - Middle: Tabbed view (Overview | MH Summary | Press Summary)
  - Bottom: Quick action buttons (Export Reports, User Management)
- **Pattern:** Tabs use JavaScript to toggle content sections
- **Navigation:** Links to specific analytics, reports, user management

**File:** `PlantManager/mh-analytics.html`
- **Purpose:** Material handling deep dive (same as MH Lead)
- **Charts:** Same 4 charts as MaterialHandlerLead/analytics.html
- **Additional:** Cross-site comparison (Expo Drive vs VITS Drive) toggle
- **Pattern:** Clone MaterialHandlerLead/analytics.html, add site selector

**File:** `PlantManager/press-analytics.html`
- **Purpose:** Press floor deep dive (same as Operator Lead)
- **Charts:** Same charts as OperatorLead/press-analytics.html
- **Additional:** Multi-shift comparison (1st, 2nd, 3rd shift tabs)
- **Pattern:** Clone OperatorLead/press-analytics.html, add shift selector

**File:** `PlantManager/reports.html`
- **Purpose:** Report generation and scheduling
- **Components:**
  - Report type dropdown (Daily Summary, Weekly Performance, Monthly Trends, Custom)
  - Date range picker
  - Format dropdown (PDF, Excel, CSV)
  - "Generate Report" button (accent style)
  - Scheduled reports table (Report name, Frequency, Recipients, Last run, Actions)
  - "Schedule New Report" button opens dialog
- **Pattern:** Form layout with table below

**File:** `PlantManager/user-management.html`
- **Purpose:** User administration
- **Components:**
  - Table: Badge ID, Name, Role, Site, Last Login, Status, Actions (Edit, Deactivate)
  - "Add User" button (accent) opens dialog
  - Filters: Site, Role, Status (Active/Inactive)
  - Search box
- **Pattern:** Standard admin table with CRUD operations
- **Dialog:** Form with Badge ID, Name, PIN, Role dropdown, Site dropdown

### Operator Module (2 files)
**File:** `Operator/active-jobs.html`
- **Purpose:** Currently running jobs from Visual ERP
- **Components:**
  - Table: Job #, Part #, Operation, Qty Remaining, Est. Complete Time, Status
  - Read-only (data from Infor Visual)
  - Refresh button
- **Pattern:** Simple read-only table

**File:** `Operator/recent.html`
- **Purpose:** Completed request history
- **Components:**
  - Table: Date/Time, Request Type, Details, Priority, Completion Time
  - Date filter
  - Search box
- **Pattern:** Clone MaterialHandler/recent.html structure

