## 🎨 CHART SVG TEMPLATES (Copy-Paste Ready)

### Bar Chart Template
```html
<svg viewBox="0 0 400 250" class="chart-svg">
    <line x1="50" y1="200" x2="380" y2="200" stroke="var(--divider-stroke)" stroke-width="2"/>
    <line x1="50" y1="30" x2="50" y2="200" stroke="var(--divider-stroke)" stroke-width="2"/>
    
    <rect x="70" y="100" width="60" height="100" fill="var(--accent-default)" opacity="0.8"/>
    <text x="100" y="215" text-anchor="middle" font-size="12">Label 1</text>
    <text x="100" y="90" text-anchor="middle" font-size="14" font-weight="600">10</text>
    
    <!-- Repeat for more bars -->
</svg>
```

### Line Chart Template
```html
<svg viewBox="0 0 400 250" class="chart-svg">
    <line x1="50" y1="200" x2="380" y2="200" stroke="var(--divider-stroke)" stroke-width="2"/>
    <line x1="50" y1="30" x2="50" y2="200" stroke="var(--divider-stroke)" stroke-width="2"/>
    
    <polyline 
        points="70,120 140,100 210,130 280,110 350,95"
        fill="none"
        stroke="var(--accent-default)"
        stroke-width="3"
        stroke-linecap="round"
    />
    
    <circle cx="70" cy="120" r="5" fill="var(--accent-default)" />
    <!-- Repeat for data points -->
</svg>
```

### Pie Chart Template
```html
<svg viewBox="0 0 400 250" class="chart-svg">
    <g transform="translate(200, 125)">
        <path d="M 0,-80 A 80,80 0 0,1 69.3,46.2 L 0,0 Z" fill="var(--accent-default)" opacity="0.8" />
        <text x="30" y="-40" text-anchor="middle" font-size="12" fill="#FFFFFF" font-weight="600">30%</text>
        <!-- Repeat for slices -->
    </g>
</svg>
```

### Stacked Bar Chart Template
```html
<svg viewBox="0 0 400 250" class="chart-svg">
    <!-- Axes same as bar chart -->
    
    <!-- Stacked segments -->
    <rect x="70" y="150" width="60" height="50" fill="var(--success-color)" opacity="0.8"/>
    <rect x="70" y="100" width="60" height="50" fill="var(--warning-color)" opacity="0.8"/>
    <rect x="70" y="50" width="60" height="50" fill="var(--error-color)" opacity="0.8"/>
</svg>
```

