## 🚀 QUICK IMPLEMENTATION GUIDE

For each remaining file:

1. **Copy navigation from corresponding role** (same nav-pane structure)
2. **Select appropriate chart template** from above
3. **Populate table with MockData** array
4. **Add command bar** with filters/search
5. **Include status bar** with clock
6. **Link JavaScript** (`<script src="../Shared/mock-data.js"></script>`)
7. **Test navigation** links to other views

**Estimated time per file:** 30-45 minutes (charts take longer, simple tables faster)

